\sqrt{c}\frac{\exp\left(-\frac{x^2}{3c}\right)}{\exp\left(-\frac{x^2}{2c}\right)}=\sqrt{c}\exp\left(\frac{x^2}{2c}-\frac{x^2}{3c}\right)=\sqrt{c}\exp\left(\frac{x^2}{6c}\right)=\exp\left(\frac{x^2}{6c}+\log\sqrt{c}\right).
